    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Gill's Exposition of the Entire Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Now in the eighteenth year of his reign, when he had purged the land and the house,.... The temple; this was in the twenty sixth year of his age, six years this work had been doing before it was finished: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "he sent Shaphan the son of Azaliah: who only is mentioned in 2 Kings 22:3 two more are added here, as follow: ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "he sent Shaphan the son of Azaliah: who only is mentioned in ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
